# Sub-E: factorial iterativo con Label friendly (sin rel manual).
# 5! = 120
D 0 0 result Integer 1
D 0 0 n Integer 5
D 0 0 zero Integer 0
D 0 0 one Integer 1
R 0 0 Label [fact_loop]
R 0 0 Mul [result, n] result
R 0 0 Sub [n, one] n
R 0 0 Eq [n, zero] done
R 0 0 Jz [done, fact_loop]
R 0 0 ExitTop [result]
